<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038985" n="279r"/>
<opener><lb/>Illustrissimo et Celeberrimo Viro
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Johanni Poleno</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</opener>
  <p><lb/>Post meum in <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Urbem Patriam</rs> appulsum, qui (Deo sit laus) feliciter
                        <lb/>contigit <date when="1717-07-03">d. 3 hujus mensis</date>, nil magis conveniens esse existimavi, quam Te per epistolium
                        <lb/>tam cito quam liceret salutare, debitamque Tibi
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me pro tot mihi exhibitis beneficiis et sincerioris amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> testimoniis 
                        <lb/>gratiarum actionem renovare. Beabis autem me, si meum adver<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sus Te animum talem, qualem ab ingenuo ho<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine expectare debes, esse credas simulque nimiam mihi libertatem ignoscas si forte
    <lb/>ultra quam par est Te per rerum mearum curam molestiis onera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vi. In primis vero gratum mihi facies, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ratione futuri nostri
                        <lb/>convictus (si quidem benevolentia
                        <lb/>tua molestias hinc forte in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus Tuis enascituras superare velit) a me Tibi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>standa sunt, libere statues,
                        <lb/>et porro mecum, quamvis cum i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>erente, ea ratione ages qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> familiares decet.
                        <lb/>Prolixior ne sim tempus et negotia jubent; non autem finiam
    <lb/>antequam debitum honoris cultum <abbr>Ill.mo</abbr> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs type="person">Patri Tuo</rs><!-- Giacomo Poleni, Litterat und Dichter, erhielt als Lohn für seinen militärischen Einsatz bei der Einnahme von Buda den Titel eines Marchese und Conte di S. Michele Arcangelo und cavaliere del Sacro Romano Impero (1686). Siehe Bruno Signorelli, Poleni, Giovanni, in: https://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/giovanni-poleni_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ -->, Lectissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 
    <lb/><rs type="person">Conjugi</rs><!-- Isabella Braiola (Brugnol, Brajola o Brogiola), siehe Bruno Signorelli, Poleni, Giovanni, in: https://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/giovanni-poleni_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ --> et liberis suavissimis plurima ipsis dicta salute obtulerim 
                        <lb/>tam meo quam meorum nomine, imprimis Patrui et Fratris qui Tuum 
                        <lb/>in familiam nostram studium grata mente mecum agnoscunt.</p>
<lb/><closer>Vale. Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1717-07-10">10. Julij 1717.</date></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Oblitus eram Tibi Patavii relinquere argumentum futura<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum mearum Lectionum, id si placet hoc modo (nisi mutato pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>posito aliud interim nuntiem) scribi curabis: <hi rend="u">Explicabit</hi>
<pb facs="1038986" n="279v"/>
<lb/><hi rend="u">Trigonometriam Planam et Sph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ricam, earumque utilitatem 
                            <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue in Geographicis et Gnomonicis ostendet.</hi>
<lb/>Gratum quoque mihi erit, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exemtionis privilegium concer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nunt debito tempore pro me curare haud dedignaberis, ut et obsequia 
                        <lb/>mea denuntiare Fautoribus et Amicis meis, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>primis <abbr>Ill.mo</abbr> Dno <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Mor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gagno</rs> et D. Comiti <rs type="person">Alvarotto</rs>, cujus mandata ex voto 
                        <lb/>exequi conabor.</p></postscript>
</div>
